window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Isabel Winstead has found acceptance and excitement in the hidden alien community growing in Nocturne Falls, where werewolves and gargoyles and witches live in plain sight. She loves her life in the Halloween-themed Georgia town, loves her job and her friends and - sigh - loves an absolutely delicious and unattainable vampire who doesn’t know she exists.</p> <p>Half-vampire, half-sorcerer Viktor Hart revels in his bachelorhood. He adores his family, is a respected craftsman, drives a fast car and hangs out every night at Insomnia with his buddies. He’s never met a woman he’d be willing to sacrifice his independence for. Until Isabel and one mind-blowing birthday kiss.</p> <p>Naturally, it must be a love spell. </p> <p>The honorable thing would be to break the spell and let Isabel make up her own mind - even if she doesn’t choose him.</p> <p>Honor sucks.</p>"; 
